    - target: {fileID: 3683545945010502785, guid: d902d737a19257d4d99b52676fc479d4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_text
      value: "<b>What is this?</b>\r\nBrief description of the project: \"Mechanics
        Playground \u2014 a modular demo of various game mechanics (cameras, pathfinding,
        UI, etc.).\"\n\r\n<b>How to switch modules?</b>\r\nClick on a module button
        in the left sidebar (under \"Modules\").\r\nActive modules are highlighted;
        inactive are dimmed.\r\nOnly one module of the same category (e.g., Camera)
        can be active at a time.\n\r\n<b>How to change settings?</b>\r\nOpen the
        right sidebar (Settings panel) by clicking the \u2699\uFE0F button.\r\nAdjust
        sliders, checkboxes, etc. Changes apply in real time.\n\r\n<b>How to get
        help for a specific module?</b>\r\nClick on any module button (active or
        inactive) to see its controls and tips.\r\nThe help content appears in the
        right area of this window.\n\r\n<b>General controls (applies to most camera
        modules):</b>\r\nTab \u2013 show cursor / lock camera rotation (press and
        hold).\r\nMouse \u2013 look around (when cursor is locked).\r\nWASD \u2013
        move (if applicable).\r\nShift \u2013 sprint (if supported).\r\nScroll \u2013
        zoom (if supported).\r\nHow to close this help window?\nClick the X button
        in the top-right corner."
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 3683545945010502785, guid: d902d737a19257d4d99b52676fc479d4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_fontSizeBase
      value: 30
      objectReference: {fileID: 0}
    - target: {fileID: 3683545945010502785, guid: d902d737a19257d4d99b52676fc479d4, type: 3}
      propertyPath: m_VerticalAlignment
